packages.name: Poetry Package
packages.description: Submit a poem under 100 lines. If you have any specific feedback requests, be sure to express your specific needs on the form. When submitting, please upload as a google document and enable your share settings for anyone to view with the link. If you would prefer extra tutoring, please send the tutor of choice a massage.

submissions.specificFeedback: Really struggling with my alliteration. I want to be like the title of my favorite tv (sex and the city fyi) and have such a great way with letters.
I don't think my love triangle is believable.

Struggling with my nature imagery. My trees are only trees.
Fixed it.
I've already been to college but feel as though college the skills in crafting a college essay are integral to a balanced and healthy every day life.

reviews.message: Greg's feedback was helpful, but he kept comparing my memoir about the joys of fatherhood to 50 Shades of Gray.
Steve changes my team's break-out room name every morning for the sake our aesthetic. That's legendary status.
